Template: tv-converter/service-user
Type: string
Default: tvc
Description: User account for the tv-converter service:
 Enter an existing user account. If the default "tvc" is selected and the
 account does not exist, the package creates it as a system user.

Template: tv-converter/service-group
Type: string
Default: tvc
Description: Group for the tv-converter service:
 Enter an existing group. If the default "tvc" is selected and the group does
 not exist, the package creates it as a system group.
